name: MY SELF GENESIS
description:
I TOOKED THIS PICTURE IN UYUNI SALT FLAT WHEN I WAS 18.
I´M 26 NOW (2021) AND, AFTER THAT ONE, I´VE ALREADY TOOKED MORE THAN 85K PHOTOS AROUND THE WORLD. 
I PAID EVERY SINGLE TRIP BY SELLING POSTCARDS, WALKING THE STREET, IN EACH COUNTRY. 
WHEN I CREATED THIS FIRST EPIC PICTURE I DIDN´T KNOW HOW GREAT MY LIFE WAS GOING TO BE: I BECAME AN ARTIST TRAVELING LIKE BACKPACKER!
I HAVE BEEN GOING AROUND THE WORLD SINCE 2016 THANKS TO THIS FIRST DREAM COMED TRUE.
I´M PROUD AND GRATEFUL ABOUT MY FIRST TRAVEL GENESIS.
THANKS TO BE HERE.
KEEP IN TOUCH,
JUAN.
( @ELVIAJEDEMISFOTOS )
